<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Approved</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #28a745;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #28a745;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .project-info {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .project-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .reason-box {
            background-color: #e8f5e9;
            border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .reason-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2e7d32;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">🎉</div>
            <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
            <span class="badge">APPROVED</span>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
            
            <p>Great news! Your project has been <strong style="color: #28a745;">approved</strong> by our admin team and is now ready to start receiving donations.</p>

            <div class="project-info">
                <div class="project-name"><%= projectName %></div>
                <div>Your campaign is now live on StellarAid platform.</div>
            </div>

            <% if (reason && reason !== 'Your project meets all requirements.') { %>
            <div class="reason-box">
                <div class="reason-label">Admin Feedback:</div>
                <div><%= reason %></div>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <p>You can now share your project with potential donors and start making a difference!</p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= projectUrl %>" class="cta-button">View Your Project</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using StellarAid to make a positive impact!</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> StellarAid. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><small>This email was sent on <%= currentDate %></small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
